text:
Hello people, anybody know how can i make this code work? i am trying to make pagination to work on my site, with a template; either way I can make the anchor tag to change the url but it seems it cant change the real value of 'pages' because it comes from HubL how can i make a if statement of Hubl or something that can make this thing to work... Help please
```&lt;div class="flex flex-row flex-wrap gap-8 m-auto justify-center xl:justify-start"&gt;
    {% set page = 1 %}
    {% if settings.request and settings.request.params and settings.request.params.page %}
      {% set page = settings.request.params.page | int %}
    {% endif %}
  {% set per_page = 9 %}
    {% set start_index = (page -1 ) * per_page %}
    {% set end_index = start_index + per_page %}
  {% set all_posts = blog_recent_posts(92930847857) %}
  {% set rec_posts = all_posts[start_index:end_index] %}
  {% for rec_post in rec_posts %}
    &lt;a class="max-w-[405px] block" href="{{ rec_post.absolute_url }}"&gt;
      &lt;img
        class="object-cover h-[256px]"
        src="{{rec_post.featured_image}}"
        alt="image 1"
      /&gt;
      &lt;div class="max-w-[405px] p-9 flex flex-col gap-2 md:px-0"&gt;
        &lt;p class="font-medium text-sm leading-6 text-purple "&gt;
          {{ rec_post.publish_date|datetimeformat('%B %e %Y')  }}
        &lt;/p&gt;
        &lt;h2 class="text-2xl font-bold leading-7 text-black"&gt;
          {{ rec_post.name }}
        &lt;/h2&gt;
        &lt;p class="font-bold text-sm leading-6 text-purple underline"&gt;
          View more
        &lt;/p&gt;
      &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;/a&gt;
    {% endfor %}
  &lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;!-- Agrega los botones de paginación --&gt;
  &lt;div class="pagination"&gt;
  {% if page &gt; 1 %}
    &lt;a class="prev" href="/news?page={{ page - 1 }}"&gt;Anterior&lt;/a&gt;
  {% endif %}
  {% if end_index &lt; all_posts | length %}
  &lt;a class="next" href="?page={{ page + 1 }}"&gt;Siguiente&lt;/a&gt;
  {% endif %}
&lt;/div&gt;```
